{"tid":1020840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惡男見篋就踢　旺角「飛腳」戰中國客︰講道德都戇X","createTime":"2019-02-14T00:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T14:02:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":309,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"13e73d253f028c48608f18ed75fdaf7c5922793e","tid":1020840,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190214/photo/bkn-20190214081528680-0214_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190214081838\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190214081528680-0214_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190214081838&h=362a5b69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角是香港購物和美食的集中地，吸引不少旅客前往觀光。惟近日有人疑不滿旅客拖篋阻路，連環踢飛5個行李篋，更表示︰「同大陸人講道德嘅人&hellip;睬佢都戇X」。 <br />\n<br />\n片段於星期二（12日）上傳至Facebook專頁「香港死亡直播」，只見有男子穿着深藍色涼鞋在街頭行走，當前方有人拖着行李篋，便上去把篋踢開，有行李篋更被踢至彈開「反肚」。 <br />\n<br />\n發貼的小編疑為踢篋者，直言︰「旺角好多篋神，（踢到）隻腳都腫X埋，今日冇着安全鞋」。 <br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛喝斥無聊︰「影衰香港人」、「腳痛？抵X你死啦，踢斷都唔抵可憐，係咪覺得自己好X威」、「知唔知咩叫先撩者賤」、「唯恐天下不亂」。 <br />\n<br />\n面對網民批評，專頁則留言反擊︰「嗰班包容X出街對住大陸人聲都唔敢出，搞行動又唔敢去，遊行又話膠，上網讉責最積極」、「快啲令嗰某一地方討厭香港」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190214/bkn-20190214081528680-0214_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190214%2Fbkn-20190214081528680-0214_00822_001.html&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=4660047c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190214/bkn-20190214081528680-0214_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a2b16379b99d47f09f8b0b3072418c1a0028087d","tid":1020840,"uid":170044,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:55:08.000Z","msg":"發貼的小編疑為踢篋者<br />\n<br />\n寫交果到係咪弱撚智？小編係自稱黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1aa8158abeaf791a17bf26344569d0bcefa9894","tid":1020840,"uid":28624,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:55:34.000Z","msg":"果班所謂網民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966e8c244154fd6432dcd8f7d95c4100e6aecf8b","tid":1020840,"uid":25676,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:56:24.000Z","msg":"「嗰班包容X出街對住大陸人聲都唔敢出，搞行動又唔敢去，遊行又話膠，上網讉責最積極」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咗個真相出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600f43ffd6fe3d8fbae0130c71a87f28c26c8673","tid":1020840,"uid":207402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:56:26.000Z","msg":"網民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1105be63ad9f85d530f174e6d52af9f04ead621","tid":1020840,"uid":152476,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:58:26.000Z","msg":"香港人好暴力<br />\n唔好再嚟香港啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd293aea9d65fd323f03b7748557f825a3e793ad","tid":1020840,"uid":158361,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:59:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85dfbc4dce5ddd9dae9a8c313cbcf71b84e6aeec","tid":1020840,"uid":52943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:59:39.000Z","msg":"賤種包容狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6358b428ba63f0d4fb3325530fd59aa37a015d7e","tid":1020840,"uid":63154,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:02:49.000Z","msg":"如果全香港都係呢啲咁有火嘅人，香港就起碼唔會惡化得咁快先"},{"pid":"525e4a10db1e614f15f4b72026d5efba76892204","tid":1020840,"uid":52122,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"bd293aea9d65fd323f03b7748557f825a3e793ad","tid":1020840,"uid":158361,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:59:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"